		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know that on the Mega Drive you can get something between a triangle wave and a sawtooth wave with FM (not quite triangle, but eh - think of it like &quot;25% cycle duty triangle wave&quot;, whatever that means), I imagine you can do the same with the Master System with the FM add-on (not as accurate since it only has two operators, but at least close).<br /><br />Also you can get a triangle wave with additive synthesis, if your hardware supports that:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bb/Synthesis_triangle.gif">http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/c ... iangle.gif</a><!-- m -->

		

